'''牛頭角碼頭'''（{{lang-en|Ngau Tau Kok Ferry Pier}}）是昔日[[香港|香港]]的一座渡輪碼頭，位於[[九龍|九龍]][[牛頭角|牛頭角]]填海前的海旁，約於現今定富街近定富樓對開。碼頭於1956年落成，可從水路往來銅鑼灣及[[北角|北角]]、[[筲箕灣|筲箕灣]]和荼果嶺。<ref>{{Cite web|title=牛頭角新碼頭前百呎長木橋先建成伸展海面將在退潮時停靠|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJIa6v60AceVX&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=209&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc|author=大公報|date=1955-09-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=銅鑼灣牛頭角新航 今正式開航同濟公司午開雞尾酒會招待來賓|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFOTGaNnc3n2A&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=245&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc|author=華僑日報|date=1956-02-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=北角牛頭角新綫昨開航|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E7%89%9B%E9%